\nThe fluff of this grass is very light and has the property of flying well, so it can also be used to send small items.
\nIf placed adjacent to a peashooter, it has a 25% chance to fire a High-velocity pea instead when the peashooter attacks. High-velocity peas have faster projectile speed and higher piercing power.\nIf multiple skyweeds are adjacent, the effect stacks.</description>
